git://github.com/nkchenz/douban-backup.git
http://code.google.com/p/douban-backup/


Howto

    python dbb.py --user yourname --item books > yourname.books.xml

item can be following:
    doulists, books, movies, musics, groups, friends, recs, saying

backup books and movies:
    python dbb.py --user yourname --item books,movies > yourname.bm.xml

use 'all' if you want to backup them all:
    python dbb.py --user yourname --item all > yourname.xml

